OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA very warm
OL,6,Fand sunny evening will be followed by
OL,7,Fa dry night with some clear spells
OL,8,Fthough sea fog may drift in towards
OL,9,Fthe Argyll Islands. Winds remaining
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAnother mostly dry and bright
OL,13,Fday and becoming hot, especially in
OL,14,Fthe south. Some rain for a time over
OL,15,Fnorth Argyll with some mist and sea
OL,16,Ffog around the Islands.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
