OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FCloudier Saturday and less warm with
OL,7,Fbest of sun on west coast. Cloudy
OL,8,Fstart Sunday then brightening up with
OL,9,Fsunny intervals. Monday dry and sunny.
OL,10,FVery warm in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
